name: Amanita My Scariest
description:
Sub-title: “Lovecraftian Fungal Horror 001”

My inaugural, mycological, cosmic horror nightmare. This piece was created with amanita muscaria mushrooms and purple bladderworts.

Two artificial intelligence systems (VQGAN+CLIP) created this work. No input image was used.

2752x2752 pixel PNG
